  "text": "Considerable research on the mechanisms of PDT has been conducted at the cellular, tissue and tumor levels. These studies have been on photochemical mechanisms of cell and tumor destruction, the structural and biochemical basis of cell and tumor destruction, as well as the uptake and binding of PDT agents at the cell and tumor levels [CITATION_1] .",
